    <entry>
      <title>浅尝IAR下为嵌入式C构建测试驱动开发</title>
      <link href="/2019/08/20/embedded_c_unit_test_iar_unity/"/>
      <url>/2019/08/20/embedded_c_unit_test_iar_unity/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我们以往的开发模式，往往没有基于测试驱动开发（Test Driven Development,TDD）。测试这块以功能测试，系统集成测试为主，集成测试中也会自己设计一些自动化测试的工装，真正意义上的基于代码级的单元测试是空白。</p><p>测试驱动开发（Test Driven Development），简称TDD。我们不要把它从字面上理解成是某种驱动的开发，或者这个应该是由测试工程师去关注的某种技术。实际上这应该是开发人员去关注的一种开发模式，一种基于测试驱动去开发的模式，它是敏捷开发的一项核心技术。</p><p>以下我们以IAR下的C开发为例，聊一聊如何进行具体的单元测试工作。</p><h2 id="测试环境准备"><a href="#测试环境准备" class="headerlink" title="测试环境准备"></a>测试环境准备</h2><p>我们这里用开源的Unity作为这次的单元测试工具，有个实时3D开发平台也叫Unity，这里不要混淆。点<a href="http://www.throwtheswitch.org/unity" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>可以访问unity的官网，或者直接用git把unity从”<a href="https://github.com/ThrowTheSwitch/Unity.git&quot;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/ThrowTheSwitch/Unity.git&quot;</a> clone到本地，参考下图：</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Hsdft4Tt/screenshot-35.png" alt></p><p>后面我们会把src和extras中的两个.c文件加进我们的项目工程中，请参考下图：</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/FR1yyKRv/screenshot-36.png" alt></p><p>新建一个工程配置，专门用于单元测试</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/yxcSj3CM/screenshot-38.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/jjfKLH6Y/screenshot-39.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/cHNWYvTg/screenshot-40.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/fTVPzwj6/screenshot-41.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/h45C3kWM/screenshot-42.png" alt></p><p>添加宏定义TDD</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Y2GVkrxT/screenshot-43.png" alt></p><h2 id="编写单元测试用例"><a href="#编写单元测试用例" class="headerlink" title="编写单元测试用例"></a>编写单元测试用例</h2><p>我这里以某个项目中的，service模块下的，utility.c中的两个函数为例来编写单元测试用例，请参考下面这些：</p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/k257Vz7J/screenshot-44.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Mnrq15Gy/screenshot-45.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/f3tZCd31/screenshot-46.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7CF4WL0h/screenshot-47.png" alt></p><p>新建”test_utility.c”,并添加到项目中，代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &quot;utility.h&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#include &quot;unity.h&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#include &quot;unity_fixture.h&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">static T_U8 GetHour(T_U16 minutes)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  TS_UTILITY_HOUR_MIN hour_min;</span><br><span class="line">  UtilityGenHourMin(minutes,&amp;hour_min);</span><br><span class="line">  return hour_min.hour;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">static T_U8 GetMin(T_U16 minutes)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  TS_UTILITY_HOUR_MIN hour_min;</span><br><span class="line">  UtilityGenHourMin(minutes,&amp;hour_min);</span><br><span class="line">  return hour_min.min;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TEST_GROUP(utility);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//sometimes you may want to get at local data in a module.</span><br><span class="line">//for example: If you plan to pass by reference, this could be useful</span><br><span class="line">//however, it should often be avoided</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TEST_SETUP(utility)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  //This is run before EACH TEST</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TEST_TEAR_DOWN(utility)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TEST(utility,UtilityGenHourMin_Test)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(0,GetHour(59));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(1,GetHour(60));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(1,GetHour(61));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(2,GetHour(120));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(2,GetHour(121));</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(59,GetMin(59));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(0,GetMin(60));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(1,GetMin(61));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(0,GetMin(120));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_UINT8(1,GetMin(121));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TEST(utility, UtilityGenU8_GenTest)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  //All of these should pass</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_HEX(0x01, UtilityGenU8(0,0));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_HEX(0x80, UtilityGenU8(7,7));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_HEX(0xFF, UtilityGenU8(0,7));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_HEX(0x0F, UtilityGenU8(0,3));</span><br><span class="line">  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL_HEX(0xF0, UtilityGenU8(4,7));   </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新建”test_utility_runner.c”,并添加到项目，代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &quot;unity.h&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#include &quot;unity_fixture.h&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TEST_GROUP_RUNNER(utility)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  RUN_TEST_CASE(utility, UtilityGenU8_GenTest);</span><br><span class="line">  RUN_TEST_CASE(utility, UtilityGenHourMin_Test);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新建”all_tests.c”,并添加到项目，代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &quot;unity_fixture.h&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">static void RunAllTests(void)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  RUN_TEST_GROUP(utility);</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#ifdef _TDD_</span><br><span class="line">int main(int argc, const char * argv[])</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  return UnityMain(argc, argv, RunAllTests);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#endif</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="跑单元测试"><a href="#跑单元测试" class="headerlink" title="跑单元测试"></a>跑单元测试</h2><ul><li>跑单元测试前先确保把主程序的入口用宏包裹起来，参看下图：</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/sxM9PgTS/screenshot-48.png" alt></p><ul><li>在工程选项中设置debuger为simulator，参看下图:</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/tCPv8Bz6/screenshot-49.png" alt></p><ul><li><p>重新编译整个工程</p></li><li><p>进入debug模式，参看下图：</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/2qZdDHbG/screenshot-50.png" alt></p><ul><li>打开Terminal I/O 窗口，参看下图：</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7bdxCmf0/screenshot-51.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/RJ64snbW/screenshot-52.png" alt></p><ul><li>运行结果：</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/hhfDPHPK/screenshot-53.png" alt></p>]]></content>
      
      
